					<p>The profile you create on our Site will be publically accessible unless otherwise indicated. You may delete your profile by requesting to delete your account by contacting us via phone or by email at bookings@shyftworks.com. The information collected during the registration process by Shyft may be used by Shyft to: contact members, customize content to match your preferences, display member status, and display the date of a member’s last visit</<p>p>

