					<h4>c. Affiliates and Acquisitions.</h4>
					<p>We may share some or all of your Personal Information with our parent company, subsidiaries, joint ventures, or other companies under a common control (“Affiliates”), in which case we will require our Affiliates to honor this Privacy Policy. As described above, Shyft complies with the U.S.—E.U. Safe Harbor Framework. If another company acquires our company, business, or our assets, that company will possess the Personal Information collected by us and will assume the rights and obligations regarding your Personal Information as described in this Privacy Policy. You will be notified via email and/or a prominent notice on our Site of any change in ownership or uses of your Personal Information, as well as any choices you may have regarding your Personal Information.</p>

					<h4>d. Other Disclosures.</h4>
